{
  "name": "Tool Materials",
  "category": "tfc:bsa",
  "icon": "minecraft:flint",
  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "Better Stone Age adds many new stone types for you to make tools out of, both practical and impractical.$(br2)Contents:$(br)$(l:tfc:bsa/tool_materials#flint)Flint$()$(br)$(l:tfc:bsa/tool_materials#obsidian)Obsidian$()$(br)$(l:tfc:bsa/tool_materials#precious_gems)Precious Gems$()"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "item": {
        "item": "minecraft:flint"
      },
      "text": "$(thing)Flint$() is a rare and valuable rock that can be found submerged in freshwater lakes.$(br)$(br)This is the only way to obtain it, as it is no longer dropped by gravel.",
      "anchor": "flint"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "name": "Flint",
      "multiblock": {
        "mapping": {
          "0": "tfc:groundcover/flint",
          "G": "tfc:rock/gravel/chert"
        },
        "pattern": [
          ["0"],
          ["G"]
        ]
      },
      "enable_visualize": false
    },
    {
      "type": "tfc:knapping_recipe",
      "recipe": "bsa:rock_knapping/stone/axe_head/flint",
      "text": "Like stone, flint can be knapped into tool heads. Flint tools are slightly stronger than stone tools, but worse than copper ones."
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "item": {
        "item": "bsa:obsidian"
      },
      "text": "Obsidian is another useful material from which to make tool heads. It can be found near volcanoes.",
      "anchor": "obsidian"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "name": "Obsidian",
      "multiblock": {
        "mapping": {
          "0": "bsa:groundcover/obsidian",
          "G": "tfc:rock/raw/basalt"
        },
        "pattern": [
          ["0"],
          ["G"]
        ]
      },
      "enable_visualize": false
    },
    {
      "type": "tfc:knapping_recipe",
      "recipe": "bsa:rock_knapping/stone/shovel_head/obsidian",
      "text": "Obsidian tools mine faster and deal more damage than all other types of stone tools, but are also extremely fragile, with very low durability."
    },
    {
      "type": "tfc:knapping_recipe",
      "recipe": "bsa:rock_knapping/stone/hoe_head_2/topaz",
      "text": "Precious gemstones can also be knapped into tool heads, but these tools are only as effective as standard stone tools.",
      "anchor": "precious_gems"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "bsa:crafting/stone/axe/flint/no_binding",
      "recipe2": "bsa:crafting/stone/axe/diamond/strong_binding"
    },
    {
      "type": "tfc:knapping_recipe",
      "recipe": "bsa:rock_knapping/stone/multitool_head/obsidian",
      "text": "These new tools can also have $(l:tfc:bsa/tool_bindings)Tool Bindings$() and be crafted with $(l:tfc:bsa/multitool)Multitools$()."
    }
  ],
